OL,3,CWhat will PM Andy Burnham mean for
OL,4,CCumbria and the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FSir Keir won a landslide at the
OL,7,Fgeneral election in July 2024, but his
OL,8,Fpremiership was marked by a series of
OL,9,Fu-turns, controversies and setbacks
OL,10,Ffor Labour, including at the Scottish
OL,11,FParliament election in May.
OL,13,FHe announced his resignation on 22
OL,14,FJune.
OL,16,FThat was the same day Mr Burnham was
OL,17,Fsworn in as an MP after winning a by-
OL,18,Felection in Makerfield, Greater
OL,19,FManchester.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
