OL,3,CWhat will PM Andy Burnham mean for
OL,4,CCumbria and the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FHe was Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,7,Ffrom 2017 until his return to
OL,8,Fparliament.
OL,10,FHe previously served as Culture
OL,11,FSecretary and Health Secretary between
OL,12,F2008 and 2010, and stood
OL,13,Funsuccessfully to be Labour leader in
OL,14,F2010 and 2015.
OL,16,FAnalysis from our Political
OL,17,FCorrespondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
