OL,3,CWhat will PM Andy Burnham mean for
OL,4,CCumbria and the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has already received a
OL,7,Fshot across the bows from rural Labour
OL,8,FMPs, warning him not to treat their
OL,9,Fareas as an "afterthought."
OL,11,FHe's been mayor of a big city region
OL,12,Fand hasn't spoken much - previously or
OL,13,Frecently - about the challenges faced
OL,14,Fin places like the Cumbrian
OL,15,Fcountryside.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
