OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1784726325
OL,3,CWhat will PM Andy Burnham mean for
OL,4,CCumbria and the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FAfter high-profile sewage issues in
OL,7,FWindermere and elsewhere, his pledge
OL,8,Fto "ensure all parts of the UK are
OL,9,Fable to take greater public control of
OL,10,Fessential services like water" is
OL,11,Fworth watching, though it's unclear
OL,12,Fexactly what he's proposing.
OL,14,FWhat is clear is that the so-called
OL,15,F'King of the North' is focused on
OL,16,Fhanding more powers over issues like
OL,17,Ftransport and housing from Westminster
OL,18,Fto regional mayors.
OL,20,FThe first Mayor of Cumbria will be
OL,21,Felected in May 2027.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
