SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1784726325
OL,3,CWhat will PM Andy Burnham mean for
OL,4,CCumbria and the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FIt's a matter of political debate
OL,7,Fwhether devolution actually improves
OL,8,Fplaces' prospects, but with the new
OL,9,FPrime Minister putting a lot of eggs
OL,10,Fin that basket, it appears fortuitous
OL,11,Fthat Cumbria will be joining the fold.
OL,13,FThat mayoral election looks wide open,
OL,14,Fso it will also present a fascinating
OL,15,Frelatively early test of Labour's
OL,16,Fpopularity under their new leader.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
